### Seed Bella demo
POST http://localhost:8317/api/dev/seed

### List pets
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets

### Pet overview
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/overview

### Check-ins
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/check-ins

### Latest check-in
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/check-ins/latest

### Create or update check-in
POST http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/check-ins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2026-06-29",
  "itchingScore": 6,
  "stoolState": "SOFT",
  "appetiteLevel": "NORMAL",
  "waterLevel": "LOWER",
  "energyLevel": "RESTLESS",
  "vomiting": false,
  "earRedness": true,
  "freeTextNote": "More paw licking after dinner."
}

### Food logs
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/food-logs

### Current food
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/food-logs/current

### Create food log
POST http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/food-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dateStarted": "2026-06-29",
  "foodKind": "TREAT",
  "brand": "Happy Tail",
  "productName": "Chicken Training Bites",
  "primaryProtein": "CHICKEN",
  "secondaryProteins": ["EGG"],
  "grainFree": false,
  "newFood": true,
  "notes": "Small treat during training."
}

### Patterns
GET http://localhost:8317/api/pets/{{petId}}/patterns
